# Public (non-secret) PRODUCTION defaults. Next.js loads .env.production only for
# `next build` / `next start`, NOT for `next dev`, so local dev keeps the localhost
# fallbacks in the configs. Vercel dashboard env vars override these at build time.

# This landing site's own origin (canonical / OG).
SITE_URL=https://www.knowpeptide.com
# The wiki subdomain the landing page links to.
DOCS_URL=https://doc.knowpeptide.com
